          <br />
          <h3>1. Set up the sensors</h3>
          <br />
          <p>Contact us and receive a package, ready to be placed on your field. Set it up according to the manual & you're all set.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="col-lg-4 col-sm-12">
          <img src="/images/iphonehand.png" width="250px" class="img-square" />
          <br />
          <h3>2. Download the app</h3>
          <br />
          <p>Go to the App Store and download our app.<br />Register an account & your setup is complete.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="col-lg-3 col-sm-12">
          <img src="/images/notification.png" width="250px" class="img-square" />
          <br />
          <h3>3. Receive notifications</h3>
          <br />
          <p>Receive notifications when your water level is too low. Get up-to-date rainfall, temperature, humidity, and much more.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="container" id="recommendedusers">
      <div class="row">
          <div class="col-lg-12 text-center">
            <h1 class="header-font-color">How techrice can help you</h1>
            <br />
          </div>
          <div class="col-lg-4">
            <h3 class="text-center">1. Optimizes your time</h3>
            <br />
            <p>Do you spend too much effort checking the conditions of your field? With <strong>techrice</strong>, you have sensors on your field doing your work for you, automatically sending info on water level, temperature, and humidity, among other things.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="col-lg-4">
            <h3 class="text-center">2. Greater accuracy</h3>
            <br />
            <p>Information such as your current water level is easily understandable and accurate. No more guesswork and relying on intuition. Optimize your schedule planning with previous year's comparison data.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="col-lg-4">
            <h3 class="text-center">3. Saves you money</h3>
            <br />
            <p>Our app is completely free to download, and the complete service is available for a low, reasonable price. Contact us and we'll work out a plan that works for you.</p>
          </div>
      </div>
    </div>

